                   <div class="service-data">
                      <p>
                         Account coordinators ensure client satisfaction. They connect clients and company efforts,
                         offering solutions and tracking progress closely. They solve problems, managing tasks and
                         budgets for marketing campaigns. They maintain client relationships, building trust and
                         loyalty
                         through excellent service
