                         <h5 class="title">Public Relations Coordinator</h5>
                      </div>
                   </div>

                   <div class="service-data">
                      <p>
                         PR Coordinators tell corporate stories. They shape perception, writing press releases and
                         building media relationships. Think of them as reputation managers, monitoring audience
